des:
Quotable Golf is loaded with tons of the greatest quotes ever uttered about the great game of golf! Some are humorous. Some are philosophical. All are timeless!

Just say, "Alexa, open Quotable Golf" to hear a great quote. Includes hundreds of quotes from celebrities, historical figures and of course, golf legends. New quotes are being adding constantly.
